A data dictionary linking experiment names to standard curve data

Source: R/key_standard_curves.R
key_standard_curves.Rd

These data serve as a key to cross reference between each unique experiment name to the appropriate standard curve data.

key_standard_curves

Format

key_standard_curves

A data frame with 3 columns:

experiment_date

The date the experiment was run.

experiment_name

The name of the experiment (e.g. ES BEED TAC CARD 001, QADRI ENTERIC CARD 121).

standard_curve_file_name

The standard curve file name that is associated with the given experiment name.
